name: Cyclops Grave
description: This NFT was created in remembrance of OBJKT#59666 Hickey Punks #81 | Cyclops who was burned by an anti-mutant group on 7/15/2021. Cyclops will always be remembered as a hero to the Hickeyverse and for his amazing Optic Blasts. Cyclops leaves behind his beloved Hickey Punks #77 | Jean and the rest of the X-Men. Rest easy Cyclops 5/2/21 - 7/15/21
